    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the sadness. it's the pointlessness. i spend all day just... existing. waiting for the next thing to hurt. it feels like i’m just dragging this heavy thing behind me and there’s no finish line. i don't even know why i'm trying to fight it anymore. it would just be easier if i could just stop. if it could just go quiet for good.",
